                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen energy common-source unmanned aerial vehicle-mounted transient electromagnetic detection system and electromagnetic emission method thereof",
                    "氢能共源型无人机载瞬变电磁探测系统及其电磁发射方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "A hydrogen energy common source type unmanned aerial vehicle-mounted transient electromagnetic detection system comprises an air main operation device and a ground auxiliary device, the air main operation device comprises a large-load hydrogen power unmanned aerial vehicle, a composite power supply mother system and a lightweight pod, the composite power supply mother system is loaded on the large-load hydrogen power unmanned aerial vehicle, and the lightweight pod is loaded on the large-load hydrogen power unmanned aerial vehicle. The power supply is used for supplying power to the large-load hydrogen-powered unmanned aerial vehicle and the light-weight pod, and the light-weight pod is installed on the lower portion of the large-load hydrogen-powered unmanned aerial vehicle through a fixing assembly; the ground auxiliary device comprises a ground communication station and a mobile hydrogen refueling station, the ground communication station is in wireless communication connection with the large-load hydrogen power unmanned aerial vehicle and the lightweight pod, and the mobile hydrogen refueling station provides hydrogen for a hydrogen storage tank of the unmanned aerial vehicle. The system has the advantages that the energy supply mode is more energy-saving, the energy distribution mode is more reasonable, light-weight production and long-endurance operation of the hydrogen energy common-source unmanned aerial vehicle transient electromagnetic detection system are achieved, and meanwhile low carbon and environmental protection during construction are guaranteed."
                },
                {
                    "p": "一种氢能共源型无人机载瞬变电磁探测系统，包括空中主作业装置和地面辅助装置，所述空中主作业装置包括大载荷氢动力无人机、复合供电母系统和轻量化吊舱，所述复合供电母系统装载于所述大载荷氢动力无人机上，为所述大载荷氢动力无人机和轻量化吊舱供电，所述轻量化吊舱通过固定组件安装于所述大载荷氢动力无人机下部；所述地面辅助装置包括地面通信站和移动式加氢站，所述地面通信站与所述大载荷氢动力无人机和轻量化吊舱无线通信连接，所述移动式加氢站为无人机储氢罐提供氢气。其有益效果是：能量供给方式更节能，能量分配方式更合理，实现了氢能共源型无人机载瞬变电磁探测系统的轻量化生产、长航时作业，同时还保证了施工时的低碳与环保。"
                }
            ]
